{"tid":1706439,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警方否認高層下令胡亂開槍　強調所有警察要為自己行為負責","createTime":"2019-11-11T05:45:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T06:13:51.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8a40f5af6c7d08470eeae6cd2715d9de8f6e268c","tid":1706439,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T05:45:20.000Z","msg":"今日多區都有示威者堵路及警民衝突，警方證實有警員在西灣河開槍並擊中一名男子，在沙田和東涌執勤時亦有警員曾拔出配槍及擎槍。有指警方高層已經下令警員今日可胡亂開槍，警方表示絕無此事，強調警員使用槍械有嚴格指引，所有警察都必須為自己的執法和行為負責。<br />\n<br />\n警隊強烈呼籲激進示威者冷靜及保持理性，切勿作出傷害他人的行為，亦呼籲其他示威者及在場市民，切勿阻礙警方執法。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.post852.com/290341/【黎明行動】警方否認高層下令胡亂開槍%E3%80%80強調所/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F290341%2F%E3%80%90%E9%BB%8E%E6%98%8E%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95%E3%80%91%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E5%90%A6%E8%AA%8D%E9%AB%98%E5%B1%A4%E4%B8%8B%E4%BB%A4%E8%83%A1%E4%BA%82%E9%96%8B%E6%A7%8D%25E3%2580%2580%E5%BC%B7%E8%AA%BF%E6%89%80%2F&d=30k2sE%2FAiGmcVOPaBnjddROHaT3cO7pga%2FagQaCgUd0%3D&h=6aac843e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.post852.com/290341/【黎明行動】警方否認高層下令胡亂開槍%E3%80%80強調所/</a>"},{"pid":"235dd01194870a74fe85122125f19c48e90624da","tid":1706439,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T05:46:34.000Z","msg":"引狗無差別襲擊準時返工打工仔，以後無人返工了<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1703964\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1703964</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f498ea89aa2bb67859e5a0f9d9896c101efc455a","tid":1706439,"uid":108236,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T05:47:20.000Z","msg":"Condom狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36e3bbfbfba7b069270b0ad98530dd01431fbea1","tid":1706439,"uid":68689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T05:49:14.000Z","msg":"交通警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hk